OL,4,Clived apart exposed by holiday pics
OL,6,FA benefit-swindling couple who claimed
OL,7,Fthey lived apart to con the taxpayer
OL,8,Fout of more than #50,000 blew their
OL,9,Fown cover by posting holiday photos of
OL,10,Fthemselves together online.
OL,12,FAlan Forsythe, 37, and wife Jemma, 36,
OL,13,Flived together at their family home in
OL,14,FBlackpool between 2019 and 2023, along
OL,15,Fwith their two children and Jemma's
OL,16,Fchildren from a previous relationship.
OL,18,FBut they were lying to the Department
OL,19,Ffor Work and Pensions (DWP) - claiming
OL,20,Fthey were separated and lived apart.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
