OL,6,FTheir lies were exposed when officers
OL,7,Fat the DWP saw social media posts of
OL,8,Fholiday photos in which the pair were
OL,9,Fclearly a married couple.
OL,11,FPreston Crown Court heard how in
OL,12,FFebruary 2019, Alan Forsythe made a
OL,13,Fclaim for Universal Credit, claiming
OL,14,Fhe was living alone at a flat in
OL,15,FBlackpool.
OL,17,FHe continued to claim until October
OL,18,F2019, when he closed down the claim,
OL,19,Fbut in January 2022 he signed on again
OL,20,F- this time claiming to be a single
OL,21,Fdad to a child who was living with him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
