OL,6,FHe continued to claim Universal Credit
OL,7,Fon that basis until July 2023, the
OL,8,Fcourt heard. In total, Mr Forsythe
OL,9,Fclaimed #3,182.27 he was not entitled
OL,10,Fto.
OL,12,FHis wife Jemma Forsythe, who now uses
OL,13,Fher maiden name of O'Malley, made a
OL,14,Fclaim with the DWP in June 2020, also
OL,15,Fclaiming to be a single parent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
