OL,6,FShe claimed she was living with her
OL,7,Ffour children but failed to report
OL,8,Fthat her husband was also living at
OL,9,Fthe family home - and working full
OL,10,Ftime. She continued the lie until June
OL,11,F2023, fraudulently claiming
OL,12,F#49,007.91, the court heard.
OL,14,FEach claimant signed a declaration
OL,15,Fstating the information they had
OL,16,Fprovided was true, and committing to
OL,17,Finform the DWP of any changes in
OL,18,Fcircumstances.
