OL,6,FJemma also had a previous conviction
OL,7,Ffor failing to notify the DWP of a
OL,8,Fchange in circumstances, dating back
OL,9,Fto 2014, the court was told.
OL,11,FThe DWP launched an investigation and
OL,12,Fdiscovered social media posts in which
OL,13,Fthe pair were obviously still a
OL,14,Fmarried couple. They made further
OL,15,Finquiries, looking at bank statements
OL,16,Fand credit references, before inviting
OL,17,Fthem to be interviewed in June 2023.
