OL,6,FOn 14 June, Mr Forsythe attended St
OL,7,FAnnes Jobcentre where he claimed he
OL,8,Fwas 'sofa surfing' after splitting up
OL,9,Fwith Jemma.
OL,11,FOn 26 June, Mrs Forsythe attended the
OL,12,Fsame Jobcentre and told investigators
OL,13,Fthey had separated but not yet
OL,14,Fdivorced. The pair later pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to fraud.
