OL,6,FIn September 2024, Alan Forsythe was
OL,7,Fjailed for four years after he was
OL,8,Finvolved in a brutal attack which left
OL,9,Fa man with life changing injuries. He
OL,10,Fappeared at Preston Crown Court to
OL,11,Fface fraud charges on a prison video
OL,12,Flink.
OL,14,FHis barrister Anthony Parkinson said
OL,15,Fhe accepted he would face an immediate
OL,16,Fcustodial sentence but was extremely
OL,17,Fconcerned about the impact on his
OL,18,Fchildren if their mother was also sent
OL,19,Fto prison.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
