OL,7,FUnsworth, said her client has a strong
OL,8,Fwork ethic and is trying to tackle her
OL,9,Fdebts through her work as a care
OL,10,Fassistant.
OL,12,FShe has since separated from her
OL,13,Fhusband and begun divorce proceedings,
OL,14,Fshe added.
