OL,6,FSentencing, Recorder Ayesha Siddiqi
OL,7,Fsaid: "You were both involved in
OL,8,Fproviding false information to the DWP
OL,9,Fwhich affected the benefits you were
OL,10,Fentitled to. You were a married couple
OL,11,Fand resided together in your family
OL,12,Fhome.
OL,14,F"At the time you made these claims you
OL,15,Fsigned declarations but you were not
OL,16,Fproviding accurate information. You
OL,17,Fwere taking from the public purse.
OL,18,FJust because money is public money
OL,19,Fdoes not make this any less serious."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
