OL,6,F"I have heard about the pressure you
OL,7,Fwere under and that you are now
OL,8,Fworking and taking steps to address
OL,9,Fyour mental health. You recognise you
OL,10,Fneed to work on this debt problem.
OL,12,F"Taking money is not the solution.
OL,13,FYour children deserve better than this
OL,14,F- this is no example to set them. They
OL,15,Fare today facing the prospect of both
OL,16,Fparents being in prison. Their rights
OL,17,Fare very important to this court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
