OL,6,F"If it wasn't for those children I
OL,7,Fwould be sending you to prison right
OL,8,Fnow. Because of those children I am
OL,9,Fgoing to suspend the sentence."
OL,11,FShe sentenced Mrs Forsythe, of Foxdale
OL,12,FAvenue, Blackpool, to 21 months
OL,13,Fsuspended for two years with 10 days
OL,14,Frehabilitation activity requirements
OL,15,Fand a curfew from 9pm to 7am for the
OL,16,Fnext six months.
